snippet: Real Madrid overcame some uncharacteristic poor finishing from Cristiano Ronaldo to beat Osasuna, 2-0, in the opening leg of their Copa del Rey Round of 16 game.
abstract: Real Madrid beats Osasuna, 2-0, in the opening leg of their Copa del Rey Round of 16 game; other soccer news noted.
